title: Muscle, Tendon or Joint Contracture Disorder SNOMED CT
purpose: (Clinical Focus: Contracture of any muscle, tendon or joint.),(Data Element Scope: Conditions related to contracture that may impair mobility and qualify a patient for non-emergency transport as defined by U.S. Centers for Medicare and Medicaid.),(Inclusion Criteria: Contracture of any muscle, tendon or joint.),(Exclusion Criteria: No exclusions.)
